'''磷酸二氢锂'''是一種[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，屬於[[磷酸二氢鹽|磷酸二氢鹽]]，由[[鋰|鋰]]、[[磷|磷]]、[[氧|氧]]、[[氫|氫]]組成，化學式為LiH<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub>。磷酸二氢锂可用于[[锂离子电池|锂离子电池]]材料的制造。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Materials Science: Materials in Electronics|volume=31|issue=5|language=en|issn=0957-4522|date=2020-03|pages=4083–4091|doi=10.1007/s10854-020-02955-1|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10854-020-02955-1|title=Preparation of FePO4 and LiH2PO4 from cathode mixture materials of scrapped LiFePO4 batteries|accessdate=2020-04-19|author=Yongzhi Chen, Lihua Wang, Hao He, Jian Li, Yimin Li, Rutie Liu, Dongyang Li, Zheyu He}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemistry of Materials|volume=21|issue=6|language=en|issn=0897-4756|date=2009-03-24|pages=1096–1107|doi=10.1021/cm803259x|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/cm803259x|title=Ionothermal Synthesis of Tailor-Made LiFePO 4 Powders for Li-Ion Battery Applications|accessdate=2020-04-19|author=N. Recham, L. Dupont, M. Courty, K. Djellab, D. Larcher, M. Armand, J.-M. Tarascon}}</ref>

==制備==
[[磷酸|磷酸]]和[[氢氧化鋰|氢氧化鋰]]反应，溶液pH为2.0~2.8时，即得到磷酸二氫鋰：<ref>姚开林, 金鹏, 霍立明, 涂明江, 黄春莲, 张春明. 电池级磷酸二氢锂的制备方法, 2008. CN 101269806 A.</ref>
:H<sub>3</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> + LiOH → LiH<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub>
[[磷酸锂|磷酸锂]]和磷酸的反应也能得到磷酸二氢锂。<ref>吴建江. 磷酸锂塔皮制备磷酸二氢锂工艺探讨. 新疆有色金属, 2012(S1):124-125.</ref>

